{
  "texts": [
    "Bietti et al. [165] addressed the tradeoff between privacy and model accuracy by introducing Personalized-Private-SGD (PPSGD) to personalize local models while preserving privacy.",
    "Zhang et al.",
    "in [166] studied client-level differential privacy (DP) for federated learning, highlighting the superiority of difference clipping.",
    "proposed FedSPA in [167], a sparsificationbased privacy mechanism.",
    "presented Locally Differential Private Federated Learning in [168], focusing on adaptive range perturbation."
  ]
}